column5: Hi My name is G-Man, I am Spincast's son and I am happy to be on the board. I love fishing and reading all the posts. I really just started to fish this year. This is my biggest to date (bigger than Dad's this year )  I went on a Charter with my dad and Fishhunter and had a lot of fun too. Dad and I are hoping to hit Lake O and Long Point a few times this year
Welcome G-man.  That's a big fish you have there

Welcome to the board G-man, it is really nice to see you taking an intrest in fishing and you have a good teacher there but I'm sure you will be teaching him a few tricks in the very near future! Keep posting and remember, we love lots of pictures (especially when your fish are bigger than dad's)
Atta boy G-man !! You show your pops how its done Welcome to our board
Welcome G-Man!! Hopefully we get some more of those beauties tomorrow!  Get a good night's sleep buddy!!
Welcome! Your grammar and spelling are better than a lot of people two and three times your age, if my Facebook experience tells me anything. It's nice to see. Almost as nice as your fish.

Welcome aboard G-Man. I remember the post with that pic from your dad, that's a real nice fish and it's always nice to catch something bigger then your father that's forsure. Can't wait to see some more fish you get in the future.
Ha! Mum's a teacher .........gotta go through the editor

Welcome aboard Gman One thing I can really say is that your a trooper, well mannered, and fun to have on board. Ok thats three things.  Keep up the good work, and for gods sake, dont outfish your dad too often
